of bluff, bluster and blunder!]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131411176.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Despite ongoing Iran peace talks, Donald Trump celebrated Republican primary victories, asserting his party dominance. Meanwhile, his administration faced legal challenges and criticism over various projects, including a proposed triumphal arch and a new $250 bill design. Trump also reacted furiously to a judge's order removing his name from the Kennedy Center, threatening to withdraw his leadership.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trumpiana-battle-of-bluff-bluster-and-blunder/articleshow/131411176.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trumpiana-battle-of-bluff-bluster-and-blunder/articleshow/131411176.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-30T20:08:41+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Arun Kumar</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131411229,imgsize-692321.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Is Rs 5 crore enough for NRIs to return to India from the US? Former Meta techie who moved to Bengaluru says 'don't chase...']]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131411074.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/nri/is-rs-5-crore-enough-for-nris-to-return-to-india-from-the-us-former-meta-techie-who-moved-to-bengaluru-says-dont-chase-/articleshow/131411074.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/nri/is-rs-5-crore-enough-for-nris-to-return-to-india-from-the-us-former-meta-techie-who-moved-to-bengaluru-says-dont-chase-/articleshow/131411074.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-30T19:56:55+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/