y food, culture]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131407758.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/halal-food-qawwali-and-live-events-sadiq-khan-urges-londoners-not-to-miss-trafalgar-squares-eid-celebration/articleshow/131407758.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/halal-food-qawwali-and-live-events-sadiq-khan-urges-londoners-not-to-miss-trafalgar-squares-eid-celebration/articleshow/131407758.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-30T16:08:25+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131407895,imgsize-112940.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[UK urges Hajj pilgrims to leave Saudi Arabia before visa expiry, warns overstaying can lead to heavy fines]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131406243.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-urges-hajj-pilgrims-to-leave-saudi-arabia-before-visa-expiry-warns-overstaying-can-lead-to-heavy-fines/articleshow/131406243.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-urges-hajj-pilgrims-to-leave-saudi-arabia-before-visa-expiry-warns-overstaying-can-lead-to-heavy-fines/articleshow/131406243.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-30T14:00:24+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131406294,imgsize-1575444.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Greek man appears in court charged over alleged plot to spy on Iranian journalist in London]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131406179.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[A Greek national, Ioannis Aidinidis, has been charged in London under UK national security legislation for allegedly gathering information on an Iranian journalist. Prosecutors believe his activities between 2024 and 2025 were linked to assisting a foreign intelligence service, raising fresh concerns about foreign-linked surveillance in Britain.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/greek-man-appears-in-court-charged-over-alleged-plot-to-spy-on-iranian-journalist-in-london/articleshow/131406179.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/greek-man-appears-in-court-charged-over-alleged-plot-to-spy-on-iranian-journalist-in-london/articleshow/131406179.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-30T13:52:42+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131406224,imgsize-123748.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Rare Dartford Warbler makes remarkable comeback in Britain 60 years after near extinction]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131405812.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Once on the brink of extinction due to harsh winters, Britain's Dartford warbler has staged a remarkable comeback. Decades of dedicated habitat restoration and targeted conservation efforts have seen its numbers rebound significantly. This success story offers a rare glimmer of hope for British wildlife amidst ongoing environmental challenges.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/rare-dartford-warbler-makes-remarkable-comeback-in-britain-60-years-after-near-extinction/articleshow/131405812.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/rare-dartford-warbler-makes-remarkable-comeback-in-britain-60-years-after-near-extinction/articleshow/131405812.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-30T13:18:51+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131405827,imgsize-74076.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[UK travellers urged to reach airports 3 hours early amid new border checks]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131406555.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/europe-airport-chaos-uk-travellers-asked-to-arrive-3-hours-early-as-border-checks-cause-delays/articleshow/131406555.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/europe-airport-chaos-uk-travellers-asked-to-arrive-3-hours-early-as-border-checks-cause-delays/articleshow/131406555.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-30T14:48:34+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131406813,imgsize-107964.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA['Will Pakistan recognise Israel?' Viral clip captures journalist confronting foreign minister Ishaq Dar]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131404527.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/will-pakistan-recognise-israel-viral-clip-captures-journalist-confronting-foreign-minister-ishaq-dar/articleshow/131404527.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/will-pakistan-recognise-israel-viral-clip-captures-journalist-confronting-foreign-minister-ishaq-dar/articleshow/131404527.cms]]